<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ArBank - Om oss</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa, #e4e9f0);
      color: #1a1a1a;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 50px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    header #logo {
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #003366;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #003366;
      position: relative;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: #0066cc;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -3px;
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #0066cc;
    }

    nav a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    main {
      flex-grow: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      gap: 40px;
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .info-section {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      padding: 25px 35px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .info-section h2 {
      color: #003366;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .info-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact-item span {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0066cc;
    }

    .btn-back {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5a623, #ffcc00);
      color: #1a1a1a;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .btn-back:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.9);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      color: #333;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      main {
        padding: 30px 15px;
      }
      .info-section {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/" id="logo">ArBank</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Hjem</a>
      <a href="/konto">Konto</a>
      <a href="/konto/tjenester">Tjenester</a>
      <a href="/om-oss">Om Oss</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="info-section">
      <h2>Om ArBank</h2>
      <p>ArBank er en moderne bank som tilbyr sikre og raske digitale løsninger for våre kunder. Vi legger stor vekt på brukervennlighet, sikkerhet og personlig service.</p>

      <h2>Kontaktinformasjon</h2>
      <p class="contact-item"><span>Telefon:</span> +47 123 45 678 </p>
      <p class="contact-item"><span>Adresse:</span> Fyrstikkalleen 21, Oslo, Norge</p>

      <a href="/" class="btn-back">Tilbake til Hjem</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ArBank. Alle rettigheter reservert.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
